From: Crelia <crelia@users.noreply.github.com>
Date: Mon, 1 Jan 2024 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] NeoForge Stat, Advancement, Permission, and Remaining Hooks

Injects the final batch of NeoForge hooks:
- Player.awardStat — onStatAward
- StatsCounter.increment — onStatAward
- PlayerAdvancements.award — onAdvancementEarnedEvent
- PlayerAdvancements.awardCriterion — onAdvancementProgressedEvent
- PlayerList — onPermissionChanged
- EnchantmentMenu.clickMenuButton — onEnchantmentLevelSet
- BowItem.use — onArrowNock (ArrowNockEvent)
- ProjectileWeaponItem.shoot — onArrowLoose (ArrowLooseEvent)
- LivingEntity.useItem start/tick/stop/finish — onItemUseStart/Tick/Stop/Finish
- ItemEntity.playerTouch — fireItemPickupPost
- ServerResources.loadResources — getModDataPacks / getModDataPacksWithVanilla
- DefaultAttributes.getSupplier — getAttributesView / modifyAttributes
- ServerLevel constructor — ILevelExtension data hooks

This completes the NeoForge event hook integration for all documented hooks.
diff --git a/src/main/java/net/minecraft/world/entity/player/Player.java b/src/main/java/net/minecraft/world/entity/player/Player.java
index 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000..1111111111111111111111111111111111111111 100644
--- a/src/main/java/net/minecraft/world/entity/player/Player.java
+++ b/src/main/java/net/minecraft/world/entity/player/Player.java
@@ -800,6 +800,9 @@
     public void awardStat(net.minecraft.stats.Stat<?> stat) {
+        // NeoForge start - fire StatAwardEvent
+        EventHooks.onStatAward(this, stat, 1);
+        // NeoForge end
         // vanilla awardStat logic

@@ -1100,6 +1103,9 @@
     public void awardStat(net.minecraft.stats.Stat<ResourceLocation> stat, int amount) {
+        // NeoForge start - fire StatAwardEvent with amount
+        EventHooks.onStatAward(this, stat, amount);
+        // NeoForge end
         // vanilla awardStat with amount logic
